<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>军事 on Epiphany0v0's Blog</title><link>https://blog.onani0721.top/categories/%E5%86%9B%E4%BA%8B/</link><description>Recent content in 军事 on Epiphany0v0's Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 16 Aug 2025 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.onani0721.top/categories/%E5%86%9B%E4%BA%8B/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>ZTZ-99</title><link>https://blog.onani0721.top/p/ztz-99/</link><pubDate>Sat, 16 Aug 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.onani0721.top/p/ztz-99/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://blog.onani0721.top/p/ztz-99/cover.jpg" alt="Featured image of post ZTZ-99" />&lt;p>&lt;strong>99式主战坦克&lt;/strong>（英语：&lt;strong>Type 99 Main Battle Tank&lt;/strong>），是ZTZ-99式主战坦克（《全军武器装备命名规定》汉语拼音：&lt;strong>Z&lt;/strong>hǔ &lt;strong>T&lt;/strong>ǎn &lt;strong>Z&lt;/strong>huāng的缩写）的简称，是中国人民解放军陆军的新一代主战坦克。&lt;/p>
